_sText:
Deathrun_Quantum
17 Traps.
5 Special nades.
4 Endings.
35 Ct.
1 T.

Traps -
1. Noob filter.
2. Spikes.
3. 1 out of 3 platforms working.
4. Spinning platforms.
5. Noob filter.
6. Fake portal.
7. Fake portal2.
8. Lazer gib.
9. 50% chance door.
10. 50% Chance door.
11. Red floor.
12. Barrel drop.
13. Stone rain.
14. 2 fake bridges and one air passage.
15. Fans.
16. Sacrifise house.
17. Ice skating on tiny path. (easier then it sounds)

Nades -
4 Sprite nades, one music nade.

Endings -
1. Surf.
2. Bhop.
3. Old.
4. Rope jump.
My second map ever created, medium difficulity. Far from finnished, still in beta but the traps are working, teles are working as intended, no game breaking bugs.
Custom skybox and texture, kudos to the creator of those.
It's also made with the HDR engine.
